    {
      "id": "PopularPost196253",
      "post_content": "Casting costs look high, but considering the amount of lock and opponent hate you will get by putting in the right value for x, this card is capable of protecting itself from removal and stopping your opponents most dangerous spells  \n  \nIf your opponent only packs [Disenchant](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Disenchant) or [Naturalize](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Naturalize) as their artifact removal, putting X at 2 (4 mana total) will keep your artifacts totally safe and you are free to toy with your opponent at your leisure. Be careful that this affects your cards as well  \n  \n5/5",
      "posted_by": "Paladin85",
