    {
      "id": "PopularPost234688",
      "post_content": "@wiseguy20  \n  \nWhether a copy of a spell is countered depends on how it was played - more specifically, whether it was cast or not. [Mirari](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mirari) or [Twincast](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Twincast), for example, simply puts a copy on the stack. The chalice's ability will trigger when the original is cast, but not when it is copied (although note that if X = 2 then it will also be triggered by casting twincast/reverberate itself). [Isochron Scepter](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Isochron Scepter) and [Panoptic Mirror](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Panoptic Mirror), although they also \"make a copy\" of a spell, actually cast that spell, so that will trigger the chalice.  \n  \nHow you cast a spell has no bearing on its converted mana cost, which will always be the same number for that spell. [Force of Will](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Force of Will)'s CMC will always be 5, even though no one will ever hardcast that.",
      "posted_by": "adrian.malacoda",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost234688\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_post\">@wiseguy20<br/><br/>Whether a copy of a spell is countered depends on how it was played - more specifically, whether it was cast or not. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mirari\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mirari\">Mirari</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Twincast\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Twincast\">Twincast</a>, for example, simply puts a copy on the stack. The chalice's ability will trigger when the original is cast, but not when it is copied (although note that if X = 2 then it will also be triggered by casting twincast/reverberate itself). <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Isochron Scepter\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Isochron Scepter\">Isochron Scepter</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Panoptic Mirror\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Panoptic Mirror\">Panoptic Mirror</a>, although they also \"make a copy\" of a spell, actually cast that spell, so that will trigger the chalice.<br/><br/>How you cast a spell has no bearing on its converted mana cost, which will always be the same number for that spell. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Force of Will\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Force of Will\">Force of Will</a>'s CMC will always be 5, even though no one will ever hardcast that.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '234688'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy76402\">adrian.malacoda</span>\r\n                                (3/25/2012 11:13:45 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>"
    },
