    {
      "id": "PopularPost297762",
      "post_content": "I wanted to make a [Kuldotha Rebirth](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Kuldotha Rebirth) modern deck, but then I remembered that this can be sideboarded into any deck. Bye bye, [Ornithopter](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ornithopter)/[Memnite](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Memnite)/[Mox Opal](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mox Opal).   \n  \nOther than that, this can shut down Storm [Brain Freeze](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Brain Freeze)/[Grapeshot](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Grapeshot) decks (although with [Seething Song](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Seething Song) gone, they may not be played after...), Soul Sisters, Red Deck Wins... and probably a whole bunch other than those.",
      "posted_by": "Ferlord",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost297762\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_post\">I wanted to make a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Kuldotha Rebirth\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Kuldotha Rebirth\">Kuldotha Rebirth</a> modern deck, but then I remembered that this can be sideboarded into any deck. Bye bye, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Ornithopter\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ornithopter\">Ornithopter</a>/<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Memnite\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Memnite\">Memnite</a>/<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mox Opal\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mox Opal\">Mox Opal</a>. <br/><br/>Other than that, this can shut down Storm <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Brain Freeze\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Brain Freeze\">Brain Freeze</a>/<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Grapeshot\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Grapeshot\">Grapeshot</a> decks (although with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Seething Song\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Seething Song\">Seething Song</a> gone, they may not be played after...), Soul Sisters, Red Deck Wins... and probably a whole bunch other than those.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '297762'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                            